{"tid":582732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得九巴今次做法好正確","createTime":"2018-03-06T12:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T12:48:53.000Z","uid":149494,"like":20,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b1513bbbabc7a43505c57ed495561649a93c23","tid":582732,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:12:06.000Z","msg":"既然九巴員工得咁少人撐果個女人<br />\n證明對加薪方案不滿既員工只係得極少數<br />\n但因為佢地幾條友既不滿結果就比左(同右)好多麻煩公司<br />\n解決左件事之後公司檢討返今次事件，對呢幾條友處分其實好正確<br />\n唔通比搞事份子若無其事繼續逗份糧咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔炒佢地對公司負面影響會更大<br />\n因為會令其他盡忠職守既員工大為反感<br />\n而家炒左佢地只係會令某d網上遊魂屌一兩日<br />\n唔會引起公關災難<br />\n就算有網上公關災難對公司盈利都唔會有咩影響"},{"pid":"4172b970b4ccda25e7cbaa716a650997352c0fe3","tid":582732,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:19:59.000Z","msg":"無野㗎 <br />\n之但係以後有不滿就唔該咪出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1f87588da59b7580aefc0830435ca71426c361","tid":582732,"uid":2429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"賠足就得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5047e76b3bbb4b62c66775f7a70f512ad47e99e1","tid":582732,"uid":9394,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"啲雞有問題 你就殺曬啲雞<br />\n啲人有問題你係咪又殺曬啲人"},{"pid":"72f981ec91e9a9498cb93e08ae291a02ae73fe22","tid":582732,"uid":48,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"只要九巴車長以後唔好為左人工而嘈<br />\n<br />\n到時唔好怨人工低工時長"},{"pid":"f80d74afca48e3b99aae73d10f48036fa8d0ddfb","tid":582732,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做得好...依件事抵哂 之前賣咁多廣告"},{"pid":"39b410e6809975a76a3b24545212ef4721a58605","tid":582732,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5047e76b3bbb4b62c66775f7a70f512ad47e9